.update_enemy_missiles
    LDX #&00  \ Per-frame: step each of the two enemy missiles (at slots 0 and 1) then collision-check against the player. Slots with X=&FF are inactive.
    LDA tbl_2B9A,X
    CMP #&FF
    BEQ L2AAE
    JSR step_enemy_missile
.L2AAE
